### Gate 4a blocker: Bun's build system needs bun binary

Running `node --experimental-strip-types scripts/build.ts --arch=ppc64le` on
POWER8 reached the codegen step and errored: "Codegen requires bun". Bun's
official install script has no ppc64le target (only amd64/arm64).

**Chicken-and-egg**: need bun to build bun.

Next options for Gate 4a:
1. Run codegen on x86 laptop (has bun), rsync generated files to POWER8
